sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as You
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant API as Claude API
    participant R as Remote Routine

    Dev->>GH: push fmt violation
    GH->>GH: CI fails
    GH->>API: POST /triggers/.../run
    API->>R: session starts
    R->>GH: gh run list + log-failed
    R->>R: classify: fmt
    R->>R: cargo fmt, verify
    R->>GH: git push fix commit
    GH->>GH: CI passes
    GH-->>Dev: green
